io.github.dddplus.dsl

注释类型 KeyRule


  • @Target(value=METHOD)
 @Retention(value=SOURCE)
public @interface KeyRule
    关键的业务规则，控制逻辑.

    对于无入参且返回类型是Boolean/boolean的公共方法，无需标注，自动注册为KeyRule.

    如果想修正，再手工标注.

    Example:

     

 class ShipmentOrder {
     ℗KeyRule(refer = WaybillSourceEnum.class)
     public WaybillSourceEnum waybillPlatform() {}
 }
